Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわッ　おいしそうだ\Nキレイだね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty.
